rComments: Has a very monotonous way of teaching. His exams are extremely difficult. The final exam was cumulative, required reading the entire textbook, which was a lot of info to remember especially since it is a history course. Had to memorize maps & dates & listen to podcasts for every week's lecture for the exam. It was a horrible experience!
He is very rude when you approach him for help. Lectures are extremely boring. He basically just reads off the slides, but studying from the slides are really important.
